---
import Layout from "~/layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Header } from "~/components/section/Header";
import { Heading } from "~/components/ui/heading";
import { Text } from "~/components/ui/text";
import "~/index.css";
---

<Layout>
    <Header />
    <div style="max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px;">
        <Heading as="h1" size="2xl" textAlign="left" marginBottom="24px"
            >Privacy Policy</Heading
        >

        <Text marginTop="8px">
            <strong>Effective Date:</strong> 09-09-2025
        </Text>
        <Text marginTop="4px">
            <strong>Operator:</strong> Jingle Chen (United States)
        </Text>
        <Text marginTop="4px" marginBottom="8px">
            <strong>Contact:</strong> chenjingle0525@gmail.com
        </Text>

        <Text marginTop="16px">
            Strata (“we,” “our,” or “us”) is committed to protecting your
            privacy. This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect,
            how we use it, and your rights regarding your data.
        </Text>

        <hr style="border-color: #1f1f1f; margin: 24px 0;" />

        <Heading
            as="h2"
            size="xl"
            textAlign="left"
            marginTop="32px"
            marginBottom="8px">1. Information We Collect</Heading
        >
        <Text
            >We collect the following categories of information when you use
            Strata:</Text
        >
        <ul
            style="padding-left: 1.25rem; margin: 8px 0 16px; display: grid; gap: 6px;"
        >
            <Text as="li">
                <strong>Identity Information:</strong> Your Google account details
                (name, email, profile picture) via Google OAuth and Supabase.
            </Text>
            <Text as="li">
                <strong>Project Data:</strong> Project names and assets you upload
                (e.g., images, .glb files, and other media).
            </Text>
            <Text as="li">
                <strong>Device Information:</strong> Device type, screen resolution,
                and technical specifications.
            </Text>
            <Text as="li">
                <strong>XR Input Data:</strong> Camera and hand-tracking access (when
                explicitly granted by you for tool functionality).
            </Text>
            <Text as="li">
                <strong>No Payment Data:</strong> At this time, we do not process
                payments or collect billing information.
            </Text>
        </ul>

        <hr style="border-color: #1f1f1f; margin: 24px 0;" />

        <Heading
            as="h2"
            size="xl"
            textAlign="left"
            marginTop="32px"
            marginBottom="8px">2. How We Use Information</Heading
        >
        <Text>We use the information above for the following purposes:</Text>
        <ul
            style="padding-left: 1.25rem; margin: 8px 0 16px; display: grid; gap: 6px;"
        >
            <Text as="li">Provide and maintain the Strata service.</Text>
            <Text as="li">Improve and personalize user experience.</Text>
            <Text as="li">Analyze usage patterns and debug issues.</Text>
            <Text as="li"
                >Communicate with you regarding updates, support, and marketing.</Text
            >
        </ul>

        <hr style="border-color: #1f1f1f; margin: 24px 0;" />

        <Heading
            as="h2"
            size="xl"
            textAlign="left"
            marginTop="32px"
            marginBottom="8px">3. Data Sharing and Disclosure</Heading
        >
        <Text
            >We do <strong>not sell or share personal information</strong> with advertisers
            or unrelated third parties.</Text
        >
        <Text
            >We only share data with trusted <strong>service providers</strong> necessary
            to operate Strata, including:</Text
        >
        <ul
            style="padding-left: 1.25rem; margin: 8px 0 16px; display: grid; gap: 6px;"
        >
            <Text as="li"
                ><strong>Supabase</strong> (user authentication and storage).</Text
            >
            <Text as="li"
                ><strong>Google OAuth</strong> (sign-in services).</Text
            >
            <Text as="li"
                ><strong>Analytics providers</strong> (performance monitoring).</Text
            >
        </ul>

        <hr style="border-color: #1f1f1f; margin: 24px 0;" />

        <Heading
            as="h2"
            size="xl"
            textAlign="left"
            marginTop="32px"
            marginBottom="8px">4. Data Retention</Heading
        >
        <Text>
            We retain your data as long as your account is active or as needed
            to provide services. You may request deletion of your data or
            account at any time by contacting us at <strong
                >chenjingle0525@gmail.com</strong
            >.
        </Text>

        <hr style="border-color: #1f1f1f; margin: 24px 0;" />

        <Heading
            as="h2"
            size="xl"
            textAlign="left"
            marginTop="32px"
            marginBottom="8px">5. Children’s Privacy</Heading
        >
        <Text>
            Strata is intended for users <strong
                >13 years of age or older</strong
            >. We do not knowingly collect information from children under 13.
            If we discover such data, it will be deleted immediately.
        </Text>

        <hr style="border-color: #1f1f1f; margin: 24px 0;" />

        <Heading
            as="h2"
            size="xl"
            textAlign="left"
            marginTop="32px"
            marginBottom="8px">6. Security</Heading
        >
        <Text>
            We take reasonable measures to protect your information, but no
            system is completely secure. Use Strata at your own risk.
        </Text>

        <hr style="border-color: #1f1f1f; margin: 24px 0;" />

        <Heading
            as="h2"
            size="xl"
            textAlign="left"
            marginTop="32px"
            marginBottom="8px">7. Your Rights</Heading
        >
        <Text>Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have rights to:</Text>
        <ul
            style="padding-left: 1.25rem; margin: 8px 0 16px; display: grid; gap: 6px;"
        >
            <Text as="li">Access a copy of your data.</Text>
            <Text as="li">Request corrections.</Text>
            <Text as="li">Request deletion of your data.</Text>
        </ul>
        <Text>
            Contact us at <strong>chenjingle0525@gmail.com</strong> to exercise these
            rights.
        </Text>

        <hr style="border-color: #1f1f1f; margin: 24px 0;" />

        <Heading
            as="h2"
            size="xl"
            textAlign="left"
            marginTop="32px"
            marginBottom="8px">8. Changes to this Privacy Policy</Heading
        >
        <Text>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Material
            changes will be communicated within the Strata service or via email.
        </Text>
    </div>
</Layout>
